{
  "stem": "6719.5",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "They talk about-- there were-- it must have been about five, four or five-- five, five ditches, long ditches, about, I'd say, 40 meters long, eight meters wide.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Big bodies that were just smoldering down there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And new bodies came in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I put on top of that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "They even created a drain to drain the fat off on the bottom at an angle.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "That's how the ditch was constructed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And Mr.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Moll was running around like a dompteur in a circus, looking at lions.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And, uh, that was very bad.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "That was really bad.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not at that time, only later.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was when my parents came.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was the worst time.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "See, I think that I'm, again, if you can call it lucky, that I didn't realize the enormity of what I saw.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Although I knew what's going to happen, it just didn't-- it didn't hit me because I-- I strongly believed that if I would have taken all these things as they were, I wouldn't be sitting here.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, a lot of people committed suicide in many ways, like, uh, going to the wire, electrocuted.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The guys on the guard tower shot him on top of it, so you were dead anyhow.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So that was is it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Or you wanted to commit suicide in a-- in a different form, you drank the water.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You got typhoid and you got  killed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I mean, if you wanted to kill yourself, there were many, many ways how you could kill yourself, quickly, or not as quickly.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I didn't say slower, but not as quickly.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But, uh, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] you know, there was so much hatred in me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "That, I had all through that time.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
